-- Terra Mauricia Specialty Output May Be 85,000 Tons, Express Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-02-09T07:50:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-09/terra-mauricia-specialty-output-may-be-85-000-tons-express-says.html
Terra Mauricia Ltd. (TERA) ’s sugar unit
expects to produce as much as 85,000 metric tons of specialty
sugars this year, l’Express said, citing Factory Manager
Reynolds Laguette.  Flacq United Estates Ltd. (FUEL)  will provide Terra with 14,000
tons of the sweetener to be processed into specialty sugars, the
Port Louis-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
